# ---- V2 knowledge pipeline: derived/regenerable artifacts ----
# Rebuilt by the knowledge-importer package: chunks from knowledge/imports/,
# embeddings from knowledge/chunks/ (deterministic local provider). This is a
# build cache, not source — do not version-control it. knowledge/imports/ and
# knowledge/manifests/ ARE kept (effective source text + ingestion audit trail).
v2/knowledge/chunks/
v2/knowledge/embeddings/
